0the%20people%20a%20chance%20to%20express%20themselves%20or%20give%20political%20parties%20the%20chance%20to%20change%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESo%20what%20have%20the%202023%20elections%2C%20inclusive%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20taught%20us%3F%20The%20first%20lesson%20is%20that%20India%20is%20sharply%20divided%20in%20its%20political%20choices.%20The%20contours%20of%20a%20north-south%20divide%20are%20emerging.%20The%20Gangetic%20belt%20is%20tilting%20strongly%20towards%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20Even%20the%20people-friendly%20measures%20of%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20made%20little%20impression.%20I%20recall%20that%20I%20had%20met%20a%20young%20man%20from%20Rajasthan%20in%20Hyderabad%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20Rajasthan%20would%20vote%20for%20Gehlot%20because%20his%20welfare%20measures%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20health%20sector%2C%20had%20made%20a%20huge%20impact%2C%20but%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20vote%20would%20be%20heavily%20in%20favour%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20both%20the%20northern%20states%2C%20the%20Modi%20image%20loomed%20large.%20The%20failure%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20use%20this%20opportunity%20to%20have%20a%20trial%20run%20for%20the%20newly%20formed%20INDIA%20coalition%20rebounded%20severely%20against%20them.%20As%20it%20did%20in%20West%20Bengal%20earlier%2C%20where%20they%20chose%20to%20oppose%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Left%20in%20local%20elections.%20Win%20or%20lose%2C%20they%20would%20have%20learned%20to%20battle%20together%20and%20build%20bridges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20south%2C%20the%20Modi%20magic%20did%20not%20work%20either%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanalysing-congress-victory-karnataka-hype%5C%22%3EKarnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bharat-rashtra-samithi-congress-kcr%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20people%20saw%20only%20the%20Congress%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20ruling%20parties.%20Effective%20and%20united%20leadership%20at%20the%20state%20level%20and%20the%20disillusionment%20of%20the%20people%20with%20the%20earlier%20governments%2C%20particularly%20on%20account%20of%20perceived%20unbridled%20corruption%2C%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20Modi%20factor%20did%20not%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Framachandra-guha-assembly-election-results-december-2023%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20What%20Do%20the%20State%20Election%20Results%20Tell%20Us%20About%20Indian%20Politics%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20resounding%20defeat%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20hopefully%20taught%20them%20the%20right%20lessons%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20The%20most%20important%20single%20lesson%20is%20that%20their%20state-level%20leadership%20in%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt%20poses%20no%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20image%20of%20Modi%20is%20too%20strong%20for%20them%20to%20challenge.%20At%20best%2C%20they%20can%20cut%20their%20losses.%20Even%20this%20would%20be%20possible%20only%20if%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20given%20to%20a%20Hindi-speaking%20leader%20with%20administrative%20and%20political%20experience.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20can%20think%20only%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Assam%20and%20the%20Northeast%2C%20the%20Modi%20image%20has%20spread%20far%20and%20wide%20on%20the%20foundations%20built%20by%20a%20former%20Congressman%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma.%20It%20may%20be%20difficult%20for%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20to%20break%20through.%20In%20West%20Bengal%20and%20all%20of%20the%20east%2C%20the%20leadership%20should%20be%20clearly%20with%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20The%20Left%2C%20which%20is%20still%20smarting%20from%20its%20ouster%20from%20both%20Bengal%20and%20Tripura%20and%20seems%20to%20be%20increasingly%20marginalised%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20barring%20in%20Kerala%2C%20have%20to%20either%20play%20ball%20or%20play%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20west%2C%20Gujarat%20will%20obviously%20vote%20wholesale%20for%20the%20BJP.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20again%2C%20the%20position%20is%20not%20clear.%20The%20breakup%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20has%20certainly%20shifted%20the%20equation%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Old%20warhorse%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20the%20Thackeray%20scion%20Uddhav%2C%20and%20his%20son%20Aditya%2C%20could%20swing%20part%20of%20the%20west.%20In%20Odisha%2C%20people%20have%20shown%20again%20and%20again%20their%20preference%20for%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20is%20entirely%20bound%20to%20his%20state%2C%20with%20no%20national%20ambitions.%20At%20the%20national%20level%2C%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20go%20with%20whichever%20formation%20is%20in%20power.%20Perhaps%20Odisha%20could%20be%20combined%20with%20the%20east%20and%20Mamata%20could%20build%20connections%20with%20him%20on%20behalf%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20are%20unknown%20factors%2C%20as%20these%20states%20have%20been%20under%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20for%20too%20long.%20As%20far%20as%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20are%20concerned%2C%20the%20Congress%20would%20do%20well%20to%20swallow%20its%20aversion%20to%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20should%20be%20given%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20leaves%20the%20south.%20While%20state%20elections%20have%20spelt%20defeat%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20would%20be%20dangerous%20to%20underestimate%20the%20power%20of%20the%20Modi%20factor%20in%20the%20national%20elections.%20The%20Congress%2C%20under%20Rahul%20and%20Kharge%2C%20will%20have%20to%20assume%20leadership%20in%20the%20south.%20Kerala%20is%20the%20odd%20man%20out.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20represented%20electorally%20either%20in%20parliament%20or%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly.%20The%20electoral%20battle%20has%20been%20fought%20between%20the%20United%20Democratic%20Front%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%2C%20led%20by%20the%20CPI(M).%20If%20they%20combine%20and%20share%20seats%2C%20they%20will%2C%20of%20course%2C%20rout%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%2C%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20BJP%20as%20the%20principal%20opposition%20could%20be%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20both%20fronts.%20Hence%2C%20the%20UDF%20and%20the%20LDF%20must%20continue%20to%20cross%20swords%20in%20Kerala%2C%20except%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20constituencies%20where%20the%20BJP%20may%20be%20perceived%20to%20be%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkerala-story-modi-flawed-understanding-tolerance%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20Flawed%20Understanding%20of%20Kerala%20Explains%20His%20Acceptance%20of%20Polarising%20%E2%80%98Kerala%20Story%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDespite%20all%20these%20strategies%20(provided%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20comes%20together)%2C%20the%20Modi%20effect%20may%20still%20be%20too%20strong%20for%20them.%20Even%20if%20the%20alliance%20loses%2C%20they%20will%20live%20to%20fight%20another%20day%20only%20if%20they%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20majority%20in%20parliament.%20Parliamentary%20delimitation%20will%20follow%20after%202026.%20The%20strength%20of%20the%20south%20and%20other%20states%20that%20have%20faithfully%20followed%20the%20advice%20of%20former%20central%20governments%20on%20family%20planning%20will%20come%20down%20sharply%20in%20parliament.%20This%20is%20an%20advantage%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20could%20then%20comfortably%20rule%20Delhi%20for%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMany%20prickly%20issues%20like%20language%2C%20UCC%2C%20CAA%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution%20may%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20again%2C%20leading%20to%20sharp%20division%20within%20the%20country.%20Having%20lost%20two%20states%2C%20the%20opposition%20will%20not%20have%20the%20strength%20to%20prevent%20amendments%20to%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%95%20indeed%2C%20even%20the%20remaking%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Decisions%20taken%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%20will%20have%20a%20long-term%20impact%20on%20Indian%20polity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EK.M.%20Chandrasekhar%20is%20former%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701853499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29221132%2FEffect-4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-2024-is-going-to-be-an-existential-fight-for-the-india-alliance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20resounding%20defeat%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20hopefully%20taught%20them%20the%20right%20lessons%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20The%20most%20important%20single%20lesson%20is%20that%20their%20state-level%20leadership%20in%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20belt%20poses%20no%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-2024-is-going-to-be-an-existential-fight-for-the-india-alliance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20taxi%20driver%20in%20Tokyo%20was%20arrested%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20running%20over%20a%20pigeon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20taxi%20in%20Shinjuku%20and%20a%20perching%20pigeon.%