0appearance%20on%20The%20Diary%20of%20a%20CEO%20podcast%20with%20host%20Steven%20Bartlett%2C%20Mr%20Isaacson%20discussed%20Elon%20Musk's%20childhood%2C%20revealing%20an%20incident%20that%20significantly%20impacted%20Mr%20Musk's%20perception%20and%20affected%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Isaacson%2C%20the%20South%20Africa-born%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bscrawny%20kid%20on%20the%20autism%20spectrum%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20faced%20frequent%20bullying%2C%20leaving%20a%20lasting%20imprint%20on%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20no%20social%20input-output%20skills.%20He%20had%20no%20friends%20and%20he%20was%20beaten%20up%20quite%20often%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Isaacson%20said%20during%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20scars%20from%20that%20were%20minor%20compared%20to%20what%20happened%20when%20he%20went%20back%20home%20after%20being%20beaten%20up%20once.%20He%20was%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20four%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20his%20return%20home%20from%20the%20hospital%2C%20Musk%20faced%20a%20harsh%20reprimand%20from%20his%20father%2C%20Errol%20Musk%2C%20for%20being%20assaulted%20by%20bullies.%20Errol%20Musk%2C%20lacking%20empathy%2C%20deemed%20his%20son%20a%20%26quot%3Bloser%26quot%3B%20and%20sided%20with%20the%20bully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20father%20made%20him%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20him%20for%20two%20hours%2C%20while%20the%20father%20tells%20him%20he's%20a%20loser%2C%20that%20it%20was%20his%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20revealed%20Mr%20Isaacson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9BDmC5u_MLE%3Fsi%3DEA_2uB0Q1IO_XqDx%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20disclosed%20by%20Elon%20Musk's%20biographer%20on%20the%20subsequent%20podcast%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20curr