o%20seek%20permission%20to%20travel%20to%20Priya%20as%20Yemen%20has%20placed%20a%20travel%20ban%20on%20Indian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Subhash%20Chandran%20K.R.%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20Priya%E2%80%99s%20mother%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-hc-asks-centre-to-reply-to-womans-plea-to-facilitate-travel-to-yemen-to-save-daughter-on-death-row-2794261%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20petitioner%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20asking%20the%20government%20to%20pay%20the%20blood%20money%20and%20was%20only%20seeking%20permission%20to%20travel%20to%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20last%20week%20rejected%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20lobby%20group%20called%20Save%20Nimisha%20Priya%20International%20Action%20Council%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20advised%20that%20please%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20there%20because%20it%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20us%20to%20provide%20any%20service.%20There%20is%20no%20single%20Indian%20there%20to%20help%20you%20or%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20you.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20people%20to%20go%20there%20or%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20hostile%20position.%20There%20is%20no%20consular%20officer%20there%20or%20even%20connection%20with%20the%20current%20government%20in%20Yemen%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20said%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20is%20based%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67544059%5C%22%3Epolitical%20condition%20in%20Yemen%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20has%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20civil%20war%20between%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20official%20government%20and%20Houthi%20rebels%20since%202014.%20Since%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20Houthis%2C%20a%20trip%20to%20Yemen%20is%20unsafe%20for%20Indian%20nat