20units%20close%20support%20in%20the%20ground%20assault.%20Several%20Merkava%20tanks%20with%20%26quot%3Bcope-cages%26quot%3B%20(metal%20roofs%20protecting%20tanks%20from%20drone%20strikes)%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20narrow%20lanes%20of%20Gaza.%20The%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20has%20shown%20how%20vulnerable%20the%20turrets%20of%20a%20tank%20can%20be%20to%20drone%20and%20Molotov%20attacks.%20The%20'cope-cage'%20acts%20as%20a%20layer%20of%20defence%20and%20is%20not%20fool-proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFighting%20in%20Built-up%20Areas%20(FIBUA)%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20an%20area%20dense%20with%20buildings%20and%20structures%20entails%20lethal%20urban%20warfare%2C%20posing%20severe%20challenges%20for%20the%20Israeli%20ground%20troops%20and%20armoured%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20tanks%2C%20armoured%20personnel%20carriers%20and%20bulldozers%20were%20seen%20on%20Tuesday%20near%20southern%20Gaza's%20city%20of%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20forcing%20already%20displaced%20civilians%20to%20pack%20up%20and%20flee%20again%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20tanks%20provide%20cover%20for%20the%20infantry%20to%20move%2C%20the%20ground%20troops%2C%20when%20operating%20in%20narrow%20lanes%20of%20Gaza%2C%20are%20engaged%20in%20close-quarter%20combat%20with%20the%20operatives%20in%20the%20region.%20A%20video%20shared%20by%20the%20IDF%20shows%20the%20army%20engaged%20in%20a%20gun%20battle%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Gaza.%20Assault%20Rifles%20(AR)%20with%20Holographic%20Scopes%20and%20Light%20Machine%20Guns%20(LMGs)%20are%20being%20used%20in%20ground%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20troops%20are%20on%20a%20street%20in%20Gaza%20surrounded%20by%20destroyed%20houses%20that%20once%20sheltered%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20the%20city.%20The%20soldiers%20are%20charging%20in%20with%20their%20Assault%20Rifles%20and%20enter%20the%20building%20through%20a%20big%20hole%20in%20the%20wall.%20Two%20soldiers%2C%20one%20holding%20an%20LMG%20and%20the%20other%20an%20AR%20open%20fire.%20A%20section%20of%20soldiers%2C%20with%20helmet-mounted%20cameras%2C%20barge%20into%20a%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fovjtub5_idf-soldiers-gaza_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20troops%20are%20using%20drones%20to%20track%20the%20movement%20of%20Hamas%20operatives%20and%20the%20intelligence%20is%20then%20forwarded%20to%20the%20air%20force%20for%20air%20strikes.%20Meanwhile%2C%20bombardment%20from%20tanks%20and%20self-propelled%20artillery%20is%20being%20conducted%20in%20the%20region%20to%20provide%20cover%20the%20ground%20troops%20and%20soften%20targets%20marked%20by%20IDF.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20has%20released%20several%20videos%20claiming%20how%20Hamas%20has%20used%20hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20mosques%20to%20hide%20weapons.%20Israel%20struck%20an%20%26quot%3Barmed%20terror%20cell%26quot%3B%20operating%20adjacent%20to%20a%20school%20in%20north%20Gaza%20and%20an%20additional%20shaft%20located%20in%20the%20area%20of%20the%20school.%20The%20IDF%20released%20a%20video%20claiming%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20recovered%20from%20the%20location.%20An%20Israeli%20soldier%20picks%20up%20a%20wire%2C%20probably%20used%20for%20triggering%20explosions%2C%20found%20in%20a%20classroom%20which%20is%20in%20rubble%20following%20an%20airstrike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operations%20resumed%20after%20a%20ceasefire%20truce%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20ended%20last%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701849600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fe1jdm8e8_israeli-tanks-gaza_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fw