%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20out%20Handled%20the%20ball%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENotwithstanding%20(a)%20above%2C%20a%20batsman%20will%20not%20be%20out%20under%20this%20Law%20if%20he%20handles%20the%20ball%20to%20avoid%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20bowler%20doesn't%20get%20the%20credit%20for%20the%20dismissal%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701849540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foq5alolg_mushfiqur-rahim-_625x300_06_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-star-mushfiqur-rahim-out-for-handling-the-ball-joins-rare-list-of-cricketers-watch-4638347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20star%20Mushfiqur%20Rahim%20was%20dismissed%20for%20'handling%20the%20ball'%20during%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-star-mushfiqur-rahim-out-for-handling-the-ball-joins-rare-list-of-cricketers-watch-4638347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-star-mushfiqur-rahim-out-for-handling-the-ball-joins-rare-list-of-cricketers-watch-4638347%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-star-mushfiqur-rahim-out-for-handling-the-ball-joins-rare-list-of-cricketers-watch-4638347%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suzuki%20Motor%20Gujarat%20unit%20crosses%203%20mn%20cumulative%20production%20milestone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701849513000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F08%2Ffull%2F1696788646-0695.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsuzuki-motor-gujarat-unit-crosses-3-mn-cumulative-production-milestone-123120600375_1.html%22%2C%22summary%