Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20first%20media%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20be%20afraid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sniper%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bspotter%26quot%3B%20initially%20observed%20Russian%20soldiers%20cutting%20wood%20but%20considered%20them%20too%20low-ranking%20to%20shoot.%20Moments%20later%2C%20he%20noticed%20a%20group%20of%20other%20soldiers%20and%20one%20of%20them%20was%20an%20officer%20giving%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kovalskiy%20waited%20for%20hours%20in%20freezing%20temperatures%20before%20he%20shot%20the%20target%20nearly%203.8%20km%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20spotter%20instructed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20colleague%20gave%20him%20the%20go-ahead%2C%20the%20sniper%20measured%20the%20distance%20and%20specialist%20software%20and%20meteorological%20data%20to%20calculate%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20wind%2C%20humidity%2C%20temperature%20and%20even%20the%20curvature%20of%20the%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20test%20shot%2C%20they%20figured%20that%20they%20had%20gotten%20the%20wind%20speed%20wrong.%20The%20sniper%20reset%2C%20reloaded%20and%20fired%20his%20bullet-%20%C2%A0half%20a%20foot%20long%20at%206.2%20inches%20-%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20960%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20%5Bshoot%5D%20immediately%20because%20the%20wind%20changes%20constantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Kovalskiy%20explained%20to%20the%20outlet.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20footage%20which%20went%20viral%20earlier%20showed%20one%20of%20the%20Russian%20soldiers%20dropping%20to%20the%20ground%20after%20the%20Ukrainian%20sniper%20took%20the%20long-distance%20shot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20outlet%20reported%20that%20the%20sniper%20was%20already%20packing%20up%20his%20rifle%20before%20it%20was%20even%20confirmed%20that%20he%20had%20hit%20his%20target.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKovalskiy%20and%20Ukraine%20say%20the%20shot%20set%20a%20new%20sniping%20distance%20record%2C%20breaking%20the%20previously%20acknowledged%20mark%20by%20more%20than%20850%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20in%20the%20sharpshooting%20community%20said%20that%20they%20are%20still%20sceptical%20of%20the%20alleged%20feat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20conventional%20sniping%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20variables%20that%20are%20hard%20to%20quantify%2C%20so%20the%20reality%20is%20anything%20over%20about%201%2C300%20meters%20%5Babout%204%2C265%20feet%5D%20can%20be%20more%20luck%20than%20skill%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Walsh%2C%20a%20former%20US%20Marines%20sniper%20instructor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20ballistics%20expert%20Brad%20Millard%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20the%209-second%20timing%20of%20the%20shot's%20trajectory%20in%20the%20video%20was%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Fukrainian-sniper-takes-russian-soldier-longest-combat-kill-19847509%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20sniper%20broke%20the%20previous%20record%20held%20by%20a%20Canadian%20special%20forces%20sniper%20who%20shot%20at%20a%20distance%20of%203.54%20kilometres%20in%20Iraq%20in%202017.%20British%20sniper%20Craig%20Harrison%20also%20held%20the%20title%20after%20he%20killed%20a%20Taliban%20fighter%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%202009%2C%20from%20a%20distance%20of%202.48%20kilometres.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701847080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fgm8gbd6g_vyacheslav-kovalskiy_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeet-the-ukrainian-sniper-who-broke-world-record-after-killing-russian-soldier-from-3-8-km-away-4638295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shot%20by%20Mr%20Kovalskiy%2C%20spanning%2012%2C468%20feet%2C%20covered%20a%20distance%20greater%20than%20that%20of%20two%20Brooklyn%2