-98158.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Ffootball%2Ftop-stories%2Flionel-messi-named-times-athlete-of-the-year-for-2023%2Farticleshow%2F105776070.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lionel%20Messi%2C%20captain%20of%20Argentina%2C%20has%20been%20named%20Time%20magazine's%20Athlete%20of%20the%20Year%20for%202023.%20Messi%20won%20a%20record-breaking%20eighth%20Ballon%20d'Or%20and%20raised%20awareness%20of%20the%20sport%20in%20the%20US%20by%20joining%20Inter%20Miami.%20He%20led%20Argentina%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20their%20first%20in%2036%20years.%20Messi's%20move%20to%20Miami%20created%20a%20stir%2C%20with%20fans%20buying%20his%20official%20pink%20Inter%20Miami%20shirt%20and%20ticket%20prices%20increasing.%20His%20impact%20turned%20the%20US%20into%20a%20soccer%20country%2C%20according%20to%20Time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Ffootball%2Ftop-stories%2Flionel-messi-named-times-athlete-of-the-year-for-2023%2Farticleshow%2F105776070.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20'North%20vs%20South'%20Debate%20That%20Prompted%20PM's%20Tweet%20With%20Emojis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20DMK%20MP's%20'Gaumutra%20states'%20remark%20in%20Parliament%20has%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20'North%20vs%20South'%20debate%20that%20has%20been%20raging%20since%20the%20BJP's%20poll%20wins%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20the%20Congress's%20victory%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20critics%20claim%20it%20is%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20where%20its%20ideology%20finds%20resonance%2C%20and%20that%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20country%20has%20rejected%20the%20party.%20The%20BJP%20says%20the%20'North%20vs%20South'%20debate%20is%20divisive%20and%20reeks%20of%20its%20rivals'%20reluctance%20to%20accept%20poll%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'North%20vs%20South'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20snatching%20from%20the%20BJP%20its%20only%20foothold%20in%20the%20South.%20The%20Congress%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20consolidates%20its%20position%20in%20the%20South.%20Among%20the%20other%20southern%20states%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20held%20by%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20DMK%2C%20respectively.%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20however%2C%20is%20ruled%20by%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20has%20backed%20the%20BJP%20on%20crucial%20national%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20victories%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20put%20the%20heartland%20states%20completely%20under%20its%20control.%20Besides%20these%20three%20states%2C%20the%20party%20holds%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20--%20all%20of%20immense%20political%20significance.%20The%20'North%20vs%20South'%20construct%20also%20feeds%20off%20the%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20differences%2C%20and%20higher%20GDP%2C%20higher%20literacy%20rates%20and%20lower%20population%20in%20southern%20states.%20Those%20pushing%20the%20'north%20vs%20south'%20argument%20also%20point%20to%20migration%20from%20the%20northern%20states%20to%20southern%20states%20for%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Flashpoint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20trends%20on%20counting%20day%20indicated%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20winning%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Praveen%20Chakravarty%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20South-North%20boundary%20line%20getting%20thicker%20and%20clearer!%26quot%3B%20Congress%20MP%20Karti%20Chidambaram%20posted%20just%20two%20words%20%26quot%3Bthe%20South%26quot%3B.%20Several%20prominent%20critics%20of%20the%20BJP%20pointed%20to%20high%20literacy%20rates%20in%20the%20South%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20BJP's%20policies%20and%20ideologies%20only%20manage%20to%20convince%20votes%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20Others%20said%20the%202024%20poll%20fight%20will%20be%20a%20fight%20between%20'north%20vs%20south'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20posts%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row%2C%20with%20BJP%20leaders%20accusing%20Mr%20Chakravarty%20of%20pushing%20divisive%20politics.%20He%20deleted%20the%20post%20later%2C%20but%20the%20debate%20did%20not%20die%20down.%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20tried%20to%20steer%20clear%20of%20the%20row.%20On%20Mr%20Chakravarty's%20post%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20suggested%20anything%20like%20that.%20It%20is%20up%20to%20everybody's%20imagination%20to%20interpret%20it%20any%20way%20they%20want%20it%20to.%20I%20am%20Indian%2C%20more%20than%20anybody%20else.%20All%20I%20said%20was%20'The%20South'%2C%20I%20do%20not%20know%20why%20people%20have%20to%20get%20very%20excited%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20Joins%20BJP%20Pushback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20BJP%20leaders%20slammed%20Mr%20Chakravarty%2C%20chairman%20of%20Professionals'%20Congress%20and%20the%20party's%20data%20analytics%20department%2C%20for%20his%20'north%20vs%20south'%20post.%20BL%20Santhosh%2C%20BJP's%20national%20general%20secretary%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20always%20keep%20two%20cards%20ready.%20Now%20they%20have%20taken%20out%20second%20card.%26quot%3B%20Kerala%20BJP%20president%20K%20Surendran%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20adopted%20the%20%26quot%3Bseparatist%20narrative%26quot%3B%20after%20failing%20on%20their%20regular%20capsules%20of%20%26quot%3BHindu%20party%2C%20caste%20politics%2C%20EVMs%20and%20freebies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvi