e%20said%2C%20organised%C2%A0illegal%20investment-related%20economic%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20learnt%20that%20they%20were%20being%20operated%20by%20overseas%20%26quot%3Bcyber%20threat%20actors%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20were%20using%20digital%20advertisement%2C%20chat%20messengers%2C%20mule%20and%20rented%20accounts%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20learnt%20that%20proceeds%20from%20the%20large%20scale%20economic%20frauds%20were%20seen%20to%20be%20laundered%20out%20of%20India%20using%20card%20network%2C%20cryptocurrency%2C%20overseas%20ATM%20withdrawals%20and%20international%20Fintech%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MHA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20guidance%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Shri%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20M%2Fo%20Home%20Affairs%20is%20committed%20to%20curbing%20cybercrime%20and%20protecting%20people%20from%20cyber%20threat%20actors%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BGhar%20Baithe%20Job%26quot%3B%20Scams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20these%20fraudsters%20worked%2C%20the%20Centre%20said%20that%20they%20launched%20targeted%20digital%20advertisements%20on%20Google%20and%20Meta%20using%20keywords%20like%20%26quot%3Bghar%20baithe%20job%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bghar%20baithe%20kamai%20kaise%20karen%26quot%3B%20in%20multiple%20languages%20from%20overseas%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargets%20are%20mostly%20retired%20employees%2C%20women%20and%20unemployed%20youth%20looking%20for%20part-time%20jobs%2C%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpon%20clicking%20the%20advertisement%2C%20an%20agent%20using%20WhatsApp%20or%20Telegram%20starts%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20potential%20victim%2C%20who%20convinces%20him%2Fher%20to%20perform%20some%20tasks%20like%20video%20likes%20and%20subscribe%2C%20maps%20rating%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20completion%20of%20the%20task%2C%20the%20victim%20is%20given%20some%20commission%2C%20initially%20and%20is%20asked%20to%20invest%20more%20to%20get%20more%20returns%20against%20the%20given%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20gaining%20confidence%2C%20when%20a%20victim%20deposits%20a%20larger%20sum%2C%20deposits%20are%20frozen%20and%20thus%20victim%20is%20duped%2C%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Remain%20Safe%20From%20Job%20Scams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20always%20exercise%20due%20diligence%20before%20investing%20in%20any%20such%20very%20high%20commission%20paying%20online%20schemes%2C%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20unknown%20person%20contacts%20you%20over%20WhatsApp%20or%20Telegram%2C%20refrain%20from%20performing%20financial%20transactions%20without%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20always%20verify%20the%20name%20of%20the%20receiver%20mentioned%20in%20the%20UPI%20app%20and%20if%20the%20receiver%20is%20any%20random%20person%2C%20it%20may%20be%20a%20mule%20account%20and%20the%20scheme%20may%20be%20fraudulent%2C%20the%20Centre%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20check%20the%20source%20from%20where%20the%20initial%20commission%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCitizens%20should%20refrain%20from%20doing%20transactions%20with%20unknown%20accounts%2C%20as%20these%20could%20be%20involved%20in%20money%20laundering%20and%20even%20terror%20financing%20and%20lead%20to%20blocking%20of%20accounts%20by%20police%20and%20other%20legal%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20report%20phone%20numbers%20and%20social%20media%20handles%20used%20by%20such%20fraudsters%20to%20the%20National%20Cyber%20Crime%20Reporting%20Portal%20at%20www.cybercrime.gov.in%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701843360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ff44jnshg_online-fra