%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20won't%20let%20them%20divide%20this%20country.%20They%20want%20to%20insult%20Hindu%2C%20Hindi%20and%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20The%20defeat%20didn't%20end%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20%3Cem%3Eghamandiya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(arrogant)%C2%A0alliance's%20(referring%20to%20INDIA%20bloc)%20arrogance.%20They%20are%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20humiliate%20north%20India%20and%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20questioned%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20nationwide%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20party's%20choice%20for%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20-%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTelangana's%20Chief%20Minister%20designate%20had%20said%20that%20'Telangana's%20DNA%20is%20better%20than%20Bihar's%20DNA'.%20Do%20they%20have%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20or%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20approval%3F%20The%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20(MK%20Stalin)%20and%20DMK%20leaders%20have%20repeatedly%20made%20remarks%20against%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20Hindus%2C%20Hindi%20and%20north%20India%20is%20a%20well-planned%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Union%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20MP's%20comment%20had%20come%20amid%20references%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnorth-south%20divide%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20while%20the%20Congress%20won%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20(BJP)%20cannot%20come%20to%20South%20India.%20You%20see%20all%20the%20results%20of%20what%20happens%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka...we%20are%20very%20strong%20over%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Senthilkumar%20had%20said%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20this%20country%20should%20think%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20only%20win%20elections%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20heartland%20states%20of%20Hindi%20and%20what%20we%20generally%20called%20as%20gaumutra%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20sad%2C%20sparking%20a%20backlash%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20condemned%20the%20MP's%20%26quot%3Binsensitive%26quot%3B%20remarks%20and%20said%20the%20DMK's%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20the%20prime%20reason%20for%20its%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Karnataka%20minister%20CT%20Ravi%20had%20asked%20if%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20endorses%20the%20insulting%20remarks%20by%20the%20DMK%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Stalin's%20son%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20had%20sparked%20a%20row%20with%20his%20%26quot%3Beradicate%20Sanatan%20Dharma%26quot%3B%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701843180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fg73v23j_anurag-thakur-dnv-senthilkumar_625x300_06_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-targets-congress-over-allys-gaumutra-states-remark-in-lok-sabha-4638105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20today%20alleged%20a%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20to%20insult%20north%20India%20and%20Hindus%20after%20a%20legislator%20from%20their%20Tamil%20Nadu%20ally%20DMK%20described%20the%20heartland%20states%20as%20%26quot%3Bgaumutra%20states%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-targets-congress-over-allys-gaumutra-states-remark-in-lok-sabha-4638105%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-targets-congress-over-allys-gaumutra-states-remark-in-lok-sabha-4638105%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-targets-congress-over-allys-gaumutra-states-remark-in-lok-sabha-4638105%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Doctor%20Kills%20Wife%2C%202%20Children%2C%20Later%20Dies%20By%20Suicide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%