curate%2C%20as%20there%20were%20no%20unusual%20trading%20ahead%20of%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20outlines%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunusual%26quot%3B%20surge%20in%20short%20selling%2C%20a%20method%20used%20to%20bet%20against%20the%20value%20of%20a%20security%2C%20in%20the%20most%20widely%20used%20fund%20linked%20to%20Israeli%20companies%2C%20occurring%20five%20days%20before%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort%20selling%20is%20a%20trading%20tactic%20designed%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20anticipated%20decline%20in%20the%20value%20of%20an%20asset.%20In%20this%20strategy%2C%20the%20seller%20effectively%20%26quot%3Bborrows%26quot%3B%20security%2C%20selling%20it%20on%20the%20open%20market%20to%20repurchase%20it%20later%20at%20a%20reduced%20price%2C%20thereby%20securing%20a%20profit%20from%20the%20price%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20paper%20reveals%20that%20the%20bets%20against%20the%20MSCI%20Israel%20Exchange%20Traded%20Fund%20(ETF)%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20October%207%20attack%20were%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20levels%20of%20short%20selling%20observed%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%202014%20Israel-Gaza%20war%2C%20and%20the%202008%20global%20financial%20crisis%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F04%2Fbusiness%2Fsome-traders-appear-to-have-anticipated-october-7-hamas-attack-research-finds%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20suggest%20that%20traders%20informed%20about%20the%20coming%20attacks%20profited%20from%20these%20tragic%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Jonathan%20Macey%20of%20Yale%20Law%20School%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20paper%20is%20%26quot%3Bshocking%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20that%20informed%20traders%20profited%20by%20anticipating%20the%20terrorist%20attack%20of%20October%207%20is%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRegulators%20appear%20to%20lack%20the%20ability%20to%20discover%20the%20entities%20responsible%20for%20this%20trading%2C%20which%20is%20unfortunate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20titled%20%26quot%3BTrading%20on%20Terror%3F%26quot%3B%20was%20written%20by%20former%20SEC%20commissioner%20Robert%20Jackson%20Jr.%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20professor%20at%20NYU%2C%20and%20Columbia%20law%20professor%20Joshua%20Mitts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20paper%20says%20that%20on%20October%202%2C%20five%20days%20before%20the%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel%2C%20%26quot%3Bnearly%20100%25%20of%20the%20off-exchange%20trading%20volume%20in%20the%20MSCI%20Israel%20ETF%20...%20consisted%20of%20short%20selling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDays%20before%20the%20attack%2C%20traders%20appeared%20to%20anticipate%20the%20events%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20professors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20authors%2C%20Mitts%2C%20told%20CNN%20that%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20nature%20of%20public%20trading%20data%2C%20he%20believes%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20likely%26quot%3B%20there%20is%20more%20trading%20that%20went%20on%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20only%20seeing%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitts%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20out%20there%20that%20we%20can't%20pick%20up%20on%20but%20that%20regulators%20should%20be%20looking%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20confident%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20trading%20activity%20is%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%26quot%3B%20when%20compared%20with%20a%20decade%20of%20trading.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20traders%20are%20not%20certain%20about%20the%20location%20of%20the%20parties%20making%20trades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLinking%20it%20back%20to%20Hamas%20is%20very%20speculative%20and%20we're%20not%20suggesting%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mitts%20said%2C%20adding%20there%20are%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20possibilities%20including%20the%20potential%20that%20someone%20%26quot%3Boverheard%20something%26quot%3B%20and%20acted%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Tel%20Aviv%20Stock%20Exchange%20(TASE)%20said%20the%20authors%20miscalculated%20because%20share%20prices%20are%20listed%20in%20agorot%2C%20which%20are%20similar%20to%20cents%20and%20pence%2C%20rather%20than%20shekels%20-%20putting%20the%20potential%20short%20sale%20profit%20at%20just%2032%20million%20shekels%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20statement%2C%20the%20Israel%20Securities%20Authority(ISA)%20said%20that%20in%20the%20days%20preceding%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attack%2C%20no%20significant%20trading%20abnormalities%20which%20would%20have%20necessitated%20further%20investigation%20were%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ISA's%20examinations%20found%2C%20inter-alia%2C%20that%20the%20average%20short%20balances%20for%20shares%20traded%20on%20the%20Tel-Aviv%20Stock%20Exchange%20declined%20during%20the%20period%20preceding%20October%207th%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20regulator%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701842100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnl1tpci8_israel-hamas-attack-_625x300_13_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstudy-claims-hamas-made-millions-by-short-selling-ahead-of-oct-7-attack-4638044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20research%20paper%20reveals%20that%20the%20bets%20against%20the%20MSCI%20Israel%20Exchange%20Traded%20Fund%20(ETF)%20ahead%20of%20the%20October%207%20attack%20were%20significantly%20higher.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstud