or%20house%20has%20a%20five-car%20garage%2C%20a%20%241%20million%20chandelier%2C%20and%20an%20elevator.%20It%20sold%20in%20November%20for%20%2410%20million.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A82%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F10000-sqft-home-san-francisco-loses-10-million-3-years-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ready%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20Elections%2C%20Onus%20on%20Election%20Commission%20to%20Announce%20Schedule%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F13152628%2F3475958106_0cdd457c3a_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20told%20the%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%205%2C%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20hold%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20announce%20the%20schedule%20whenever%20it%20feels%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20ready%20for%20elections%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20EC%20for%20it%20as%20it%20is%20an%20independent%20constitutional%20body%20and%20only%20it%20can%20decide%20when%20to%20hold%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20a%20junior%20minister%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fready-for-jk-polls-up-to-ec-to-decide-on-date-government-in-lok-sabha%2Farticleshow%2F105763889.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20told%20the%20parliament%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20country%20has%20just%20one%20flag%20and%20one%20constitution%20as%20opposition%20members%20clashed%20with%20treasury%20benches%20over%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20remark%20was%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%20He%20countered%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20(TMC)%20Saugata%20Roy%20who%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cone%20flag%2C%20one%20prime%20minister%2C%20one%20constitution%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20political%20slogan%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Shah%20wondered%20how%20a%20country%20could%20have%20two%20prime%20ministers%2C%20two%20constitutions%2C%20and%20two%20flags.%20He%20added%20that%20it%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20political%20slogan%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20his%20party%20firmly%20believes%20in%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhosoever%20did%20it%20was%20wrong.%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20corrected%20it.%20Your%20approval%20or%20disagreement%20does%20not%20matter.%20The%20entire%20country%20wanted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20countered%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20questioned%20the%20government%20over%20introducing%20amendments%20to%20the%20Bill%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20yet%20to%20deliver%20its%20verdict%20on%20the%20Article%20370%20case.%20The%20apex%20court%20concluded%2016%20days%20of%20hearings%20in%20the%20case%20in%20September.%20The%20court%20is%20expected%20to%20pronounce%20its%20verdict%20sometime%20this%20month.%20Article%20370%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20the%20power%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20constitution%2C%20a%20state%20flag%2C%20and%20autonomy%20of%20internal%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20sought%20to%20know%20from%20the%20government%20why%20did%20it%20not%20conduct%20elections%20if%20felt%20the%20situation%20was%20peaceful%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20He%20alleged%20that%20no%20attempt%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20restore%20statehood%20as%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20legislature%20in%202018%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20under%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20prompting%20local%20political%20parties%20to%20demand%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20resume%20electoral%20activities%20in%20the%20Union%20territory.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20official%20statements%2C%20the%20delay%20is%20due%20to%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20local%20unit%20wanting%20to%20defer%20the%20exercise%20at%20least%20till%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20polls%20even%20local%20body%20polls%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flet-alone-assembly-polls-even-local-body-elections-unlikely-in-jk-before-2024%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2014%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20lieutenant%20governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20had%20said%20that%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-local-body-polls-wont-be-held-anytime-soon-lg-makes-it-official%5C%22%3Eelections%20to%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20delayed%20considerably.%20The%20tenure%20of%C2%A0Srinagar%20Municipal%20Corporation%20ended%20on%20November%205%20while%20the%20Jammu%20civic%20body%20completed%20its%20five-year%20tenure%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2014.%20Other%20municipal%20bodies%20across%20the%20Union%20territory%20will%20finish%20their%20tenure%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%C2%A0The%20last%20ULB%20and%20panchayat%20elections%20in%20the%20UT%20were%20held%20between%20October%20and%20December%202018%20%E2%80%93%20which%20too%20were%20after%20a%20long%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701841126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F13152628%2F3475958106_0cdd457c3a_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fready-for-jk-elections-onus-on-election-commission-to-announce-schedule-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20legislature%20in%202018%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20under%20the%20President's%20Rule.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20official%20statements%2C%20there%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Union%20territory%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20face%20polls%20anytime%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fready-for-jk-elections-onus-on-election-commission-to-announce-schedule-centre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEveryone%20Should%20Implement%20Values%20Of%20BR%20Ambedkar%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20on%20his%2067th%20death%20anniversary%20which%20is%20observed%20as%20'Mahaparinirvan%20Diwas'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20along%20with%20other%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20paid%20floral%20tributes%20at%20the%20statue%20of%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20The%207-feet%20tall%20statue%20of%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20was%20unveiled%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Constitution%20Day%20on%20November%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV's%20Ashish%20Bhargava%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20day%20is%20written%20in%20golden%20letters.%20Today%2C%20we%20remember%20the%20life%20of%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20The%20judiciary%20is%20following%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20and%20values%20he%20laid%2075%20years%20ago%20and%20therefore%20it's%20an%20important%20day%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year%2C%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20statue%20was%20unveiled%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20feels%20like%20he%20is%20with%20us%20and%20it's%20a%20message%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20message%20to%20the%20people%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20youth%2C%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%20should%20follow%20the%20values%20and%20principles%20from%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20life%20so%20that%20we%20can%20implement%20them%20in%20our%20daily%20life.%20The%20value%20system%20is%20not%20just%20for%20the%20judges%20or%20lawyers%20but%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20Vice%20President%20Jagadeep%20Dhankar%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20other%20ministers%20paid%20tributes%20to%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%20April%2014%2C%201891%2C%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar%20was%20an%20Indian%20jurist%2C%20economist%2C%20politician%2C%20and%20social%20reformer%20who%20campaigned%20against%20social%20discrimination%20towards%20Dalits%20and%20supported%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20and%20workers.%20He%20died%20on%20December%206%2C%201956.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar%20was%20a%20prolific%20student%2C%20earning%20doctorates%20in%20economics%20from%20Columbia%20University%20and%20the%20University%20of%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20that%20drafted%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20after%20independence.%20In%201990%2C%20Ambedkar%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20India's%20highest%20civilian%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701841020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fvq3duo5o_cji-_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%