ous%20superiority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20of%20Civil%20Liberties%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20veg%20and%20non-veg%20in%20the%20Street%20Vendors%20Act.%20There%20is%20a%20rule%20to%20create%20vending%20zones%20and%20provide%20security%20to%20street%20vendors%20by%20constituting%20a%20town%20vending%20committee.%20Till%20now%2C%20the%20town%20vending%20committee%20has%20not%20provided%20protection%20to%20the%20vendors.%20Licences%20have%20not%20been%20given%20to%20vendors%20and%20vending%20zones%20have%20also%20not%20been%20identified.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20a%20newly%20elected%20MLA%20taking%20the%20law%20into%20his%20hands%20and%20threatening%20meat%20shops%20and%20non-veg%20street%20vendors%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20concern.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unheard%20of%20in%20Rajasthan.%20It%20seems%20like%20the%20MLA%E2%80%99s%20individual%20bravado%20rather%20than%20a%20planned%20action.%20My%20sense%20is%20that%20he%20was%20pulled%20up%20by%20senior%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaipur-based%20political%20analyst%20Sunny%20Sebastian%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701839509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06103243%2FScreenshot-2023-12-06-at-10.30.47-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frajasthan-bjp-mla-who-shut-down-meat-shops-a-day-after-election-win-apologises%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Videos%20of%20the%20MLA's%20heated%20exchange%20with%20municipal%20officials%20and%20police%20went%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frajasthan-bjp-mla-who-shut-down-meat-shops-a-day-after-election-win-apologises%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bus%20plunges%20into%20a%20ravine%20killing%2016%20in%20the%