ap%20dupe%20to%20maintain%20them%2C%20L'Ange%20Le%20Volume%2075MM%202-in-1%20Volumizing%20Brush%20Dryer%20is%20a%20solid%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20my%20clients%20go%20from%20having%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20hair%20to%20having%20a%20whole%20head%20of%2022-inch%20extensions%20and%20they%20are%20lost%20trying%20to%20dry%20and%20style%20their%20hair%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20tells%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20L'Ange%20Brush%20because%20it's%20good%20for%20thick%20hair%2C%20it's%20super%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20it's%20powerful%20enough%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%20and%20it%20has%20a%20cool%20setting%20so%20you%20can%20set%20your%20curls%20and%20have%20a%20salon-quality%20blowout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20styler%20also%20features%20an%20oval-shaped%20brush%2C%20allowing%20for%20360-degree%20airflow%20that%20makes%20styling%20that%20much%20easier.%20The%20brush%20itself%20is%20fitted%20with%20titanium%20plates%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20a%20smoother%20blowout%2C%20and%20the%20sleek%20design%20is%20compact%20enough%20for%20you%20to%20travel%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20easy%2C%20lasting%20curls%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20an%20Airwrap%20dupe%20that%20can%20replicate%20the%20curls%20of%20Dyson's%20barrel%20attachments%20without%20the%20difficulty%20of%20traditional%20curling%20irons%2C%20CHI's%20Spin%20N'%20Curl%20was%20made%20for%20you.%20Its%20unique%20tulip-shaped%20design%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20other%20curlers%20currently%20on%20the%20market%2C%20and%20it%20features%20a%20rotating%20ceramic%20barrel%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20you'd%20find%20from%20the%20Dyson%20Airwrap%2C%20to%20achieve%20effortless%20curls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20design%20is%20really%20user-friendly%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.codyrenegar.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELA-based%20hairstylist%20Cody%20Renegar%3C%2Fa%3E%20tells%20insider.%20%26quot%3BHair%20is%20inserted%20into%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20curl%20chamber%2C%20where%20it%20is%20heated%E2%80%A6There's%20also%20a%20temperature%20display%20which%20is%20adjustable%20depending%20on%20hair%20texture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimply%20pop%20your%20strands%20into%20the%20barrel%20chamber%2C%20choose%20the%20direction%20of%20curl%20you'd%20prefer%2C%20and%20let%20this%20styling%20tool%20do%20the%20rest.%20Your%20curls%20will%20then%20come%20out%20of%20the%20chamber%20fully%20set%20and%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEasiest%20to%20use%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone's%20an%20at-home%20professional%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hairstyling%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20struggling%20with%20your%20strands%20on%20the%20regular%2C%20we%20recommend%20the%20BaBylissPRO%20Nano%20Titanium%20Hot%20Air%20Brush.%20Like%20many%20other%20blow-drying%20brushes%2C%20the%20BaBylissPRO%20Nano%20combines%20warm%20airflow%20with%20antistatic%20bristles%20and%20an%20ergonomic%20handle%20to%20make%20adding%20volume%20and%20shine%20that%20much%20easier.%20But%20the%20true%20key%20is%20the%20rotating%20brush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20favorite%20Dyson%20Airwrap%20dupe%20would%20have%20to%20be%20the%20BaBylissPRO%20Nano%20Titanium%20Hot%20Air%20Brush%2C%26quot%3B%20Shults%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20a%20self-rotating%20brush%20head%20which%20is%20great%20for%20helping%20anyone%20who's%20less%20coordinated%20and%20doesn't%20have%20their%20styling%20movements%20perfected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brush%20head%20rotates%20in%20both%20directions%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20a%20button%2C%20making%20it%20that%20much%20simpler%20to%20grip%20your%20hair%20and%20achieve%20loose%20waves.%20And%20with%20a%20%2490%20price%20tag%2C%20you%20can't%20go%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20multitasker%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Drybar%20makes%20the%20list%20for%20best%20Dyson%20Airwrap%20dupes%20yet%20again%20with%20this%20excellent%2C%20lightweight%20dr