t%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20evacuate%20casualties%20and%20allows%20the%20tank%20to%20be%20resupplied%20with%20ammunition%20while%20in%20combat.%20It%20can%20even%20carry%20up%20to%2010%20(extremely%20cramped)%20infantry%20in%20the%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israel%20Merkava%20tank%20Jenin%20West%20Bank%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f85fe7a3c8094d5d9db5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Merkava%20tank%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20town%20of%20Jenin%20in%20April%202002.%3Cp%3EIDF%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20again%20had%20problems%20with%20anti-tank%20missiles%20during%20the%202006%20war%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20when%20Hezbollah%20employed%20Russian-made%20Kornets.%20Though%20about%2050%20Merkavas%20were%20damaged%2C%20only%20five%20were%20destroyed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20IDF%2C%20which%20also%20struggled%20with%20poorly%20maintained%20vehicles%20and%20ill-trained%20crews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20version%20in%20operation%2C%20the%20Merkava%204%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fadvanced-sensors-high-tech-helmet-israels-5th-generation-battle-tank-revealed%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMerkava%205%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20only%20unveiled%20in%20September%20%E2%80%94%20was%20deployed%20with%20the%20tank%20battalion%20stationed%20on%20the%20Gaza%20border%20on%20October%207%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20the%20units%20now%20fighting%20inside%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Merkava%204%20is%20armed%20with%20a%20powerful%20120-mm%20smoothbore%20gun%20and%20advanced%20fire-control%20sensors.%20It%20is%20also%20protected%20by%20layered%20composite%20armor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20modular%20armor%20kits%20shielding%20vital%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%20after%201973%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20tank%20defense.%20Its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rafael.co.il%2Fworlds%2Fland%2Ftrophy-aps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrophy%3C%2Fa%3E%20active-protection%20system%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20the%20US%20and%20Britain%20%E2%80%94%20uses%20radar%20to%20detect%20incoming%20anti-tank%20munitions%20and%20fire%20pellets%20to%20destroy%20or%20deflect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israeli%20tank%20Gaza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f82e858e7c0c29a29dacb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20destroyed%20Israeli%20tank%20in%20Gaza%20City%20on%20October%207.%3Cp%3EHani%20Alshaer%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAssessing%20the%20tank%20vs.%20anti-tank%20struggle%20in%20Gaza%20is%20difficult%2C%20as%20both%20sides%20are%20secretive%20and%20careful%20to%20release%20only%20information%20that%20benefits%20them.%20Hamas%20drones%20dive-bombing%20Israeli%20tanks%20is%20probably%20more%20of%20a%20rare%20occurrence%20than%20a%20decisive%20tactic%20%E2%80%94%20though%20the%20IDF%20has%20mounted%20steel%20cages%20on%20its%20tanks%20for%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20important%20is%20Hamas's%20polyglot%20collection%20of%20Russian%2C%20Iranian%2C%20and%20North%20Korean%20portable%20anti-tank%20weapons%2C%20including%20Kornets%2C%20Sagger%20knockoffs%2C%20RPG-7s%2C%20and%20SPG-9%20recoilless%20rifles.%20Hamas%20has%20also%20produced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdavidaxe%2F2023%2F10%2F15%2Fhamas-distributed-a-handy-guide-to-destroying-israeli-tanks%2F%3Fsh%3Dbcdb75f34e1b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguide%20to%20destroying%20tanks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20suggests%20overwhelming%20the%20Trophy%20s