Karni%20Sena%20president%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%20and%20another%20man%20standing%20at%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogamedi%20died%2C%20while%20one%20of%20his%20security%20personnel%20and%20another%20person%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20firing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20PTI%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2W4TQely7C%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2W4TQely7C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1731988066406191330%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur%20police%20commissioner%20Biju%20George%20Joseph%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrima%20facie%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20two%20people%20shot%20Gogamedi%20at%20his%20house%20in%20Shyam%20Nagar.%20One%20of%20the%20assailants%2C%20identified%20as%20Naveen%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20was%20also%20shot%20dead%20in%20retaliatory%20firing.%20A%20friend%20of%20Gogamedi%20is%20critically%20injured%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20security%20personnel%20was%20also%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Jaipur%E2%80%99s%20Sena%20office%20in%20Shyam%20Nagar%2C%20which%20is%20located%20a%20kilometre%20from%20Shyam%20Nagar%20Police%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20accused%20the%20outgoing%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20of%20not%20providing%20adequate%20security%20to%20Gogamedi.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20given%20adequate%20security%20even%20after%20he%20reported%20threats%20to%20his%20life%20to%20the%20police.%20After%20forming%20the%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20peace%20and%20calm%20in%20the%20state.%20I%20assure%20you%20that%20those%20involved%20in%20this%20incident%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20public%20to%20maintain%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahipal%20Makrana%2C%20the%20national%20president%20of%20Shri%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Gogimedi%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20emerged%20as%20a%20splintered%20group%20in%202015%20from%20Makrana%E2%80%99s%20Shri%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20a%20community-based%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%20We%20consistently%20witness%20the%20killing%20of%20our%20Rajput%20brothers%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20regime.%20I%20cannot%20recall%20a%20single%20incident%20that%20occurred%20against%20the%20Rajput%20community%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20(under%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20government)%2C%20but%20our%20community%20feels%20unsafe%20under%20this%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Makrana%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFive%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20used%20to%20hear%20about%20crimes%20against%20our%20community%20every%20month%2C%20and%20this%20has%20begun%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20from%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Gehlot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogamedia%20was%20a%20well-known%20Rajput%20leader%20and%20was%20a%20supporter%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20He%20also%20backed%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20during%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections.%20A%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20Gogamedi%2C%20in%20a%20Mahapanchayat%2C%20demanded%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20increase%20the%20reservations%20to%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20(EWS)%20from%20the%20current%2010%25%20to%2014%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20initial%20reports%2C%20four%20people%20entered%20a%20house%20where%20Gogamedi%20was%20present%20and%20opened%20fire%20at%20him.%20One%20of%20Gogamedi%E2%80%99s%20security%20personnel%20and%20another%20person%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20firing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajasthan%20director%20general%20of%20police%20(DGP)%20Umesh%20Mishra%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Godara%20Kapurisar%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Facebook.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20fully%20take%20our%20responsibility%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi.%20We%20carried%20out%20this%20murder.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20he%20supported%20our%20adversaries%20and%20actively%20worked%20to%20bolster%20their%20strength%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20other%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D%20could%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Gogamedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20demanded%20the%20police%20to%20bring%20the%20killers%20to%20book.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20news%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20Shri%20Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20President%20Shri%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%20ji%20is%20sad.%20I%20express%20my%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%20and%20supporters%20and%20demand%20that%20the%20criminals%20be%20arrested%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20given%20strict%20punishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pilot%20tweeted%20in%20her%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B7%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A7%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B5%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B9%20%E0%A4%