0the%20security%20apparatus.%20It%20also%20caused%20some%20nervousness%20in%20the%20US%20government%20and%20the%20wider%20establishment%2C%20which%20is%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20sponsor%20and%20guarantor%20in%20the%20resource-rich%20and%20geopolitically%20important%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20hurting%20Hamas%20in%20any%20substantial%20or%20significant%20way%2C%20the%20Israeli%20armed%20forces%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20brutal%20collective%20punishment%20%E2%80%93%20dropped%20bombs%20all%20over%20Gaza%2C%20invaded%20its%20300%20square%20kilometres%20of%20territory%20militarily%2C%20and%20then%20had%20its%20tanks%20destroy%20the%20territory%E2%80%99s%20residential%20blocks%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20reducing%20them%20to%20rubble.%20As%20of%20today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fnewshour%2Fshow%2Fisrael-expands-gaza-invasion-south-forcing-many-to-flee-areas-previously-considered-safe%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520death%2520toll%2520in%2520Gaza%2Ctroops%2520have%2520died%2520in%2520Gaza.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%2016%2C000%20Gaza%20residents%20%E2%80%93%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20three-quarters%20of%20a%20million%20rendered%20homeless%2C%20fending%20for%20themselves%20under%20the%20open%20sky%2C%20with%20no%20food%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-world-watches-gaza-has-become-a-graveyard-for-children%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20World%20Watches%2C%20Gaza%20Has%20Become%20a%20Graveyard%20for%20Children%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20may%20have%20feared%20being%20cornered%20by%20the%20bare-knuckled%20assault%2C%20but%20the%20politico-military%20group%20appears%20to%20be%20doing%20just%20fine%2C%20politically.%20The%20Netanyahu%20regime%20was%20left%20with%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20negotiate%20with%20it%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20its%20kidnapped%20citizens%2C%20although%20the%20negotiation%20was%20conducted%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fpolicy%2Finternational%2F4339181-netanyahu-pulls-negotiators-from-qatar%2F%5C%22%3EQatar%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F03%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-hamas-hostages-gaza.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civilian%20hostages%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20fighters%20from%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20were%20to%20be%20released%20in%20batches%20in%20return%20for%20relief%20supplies%20and%20in%20exchange%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20Israeli%20prisons.%20On%20day%20two%20of%20the%20exchange%2C%20nervousness%20was%20caused%20when%20Hamas%2C%20for%20many%20hours%2C%20suspended%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Israeli%20detainees.%20The%20process%20resumed%20only%20after%20the%20agreed%20upon%20quantum%20of%20relief%20arrived%20in%20Gaza.%20This%20underlined%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20salience%20and%20clout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F12%2F02%2F1216715999%2Fhow-israels-judicial-system-handles-the-estimated-7000-palestinians-in-its-priso%5C%22%3E7%2C000%20Palestinians%20in%20Israeli%20jails%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20from%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20only%20remaining%20Palestinian%20area%20other%20than%20Gaza.%20Disregarding%20numerous%20UN%20resolutions%20with%20America%E2%80%99s%20and%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20backing%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fcampaigns%2F2017%2F06%2Fisrael-occupation-50-years-of-dispossession%2F%5C%22%3Eillegal%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%201967%20and%20runs%20it%20under%20police%20and%20military%20administration%20in%20the%20harshest%20manner%2C%20notwithst