20a%20public%20rally%20in%20this%20area.%20However%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20seats%20shifted%20from%20Congress%20to%20BJP%20or%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20continued%20his%20campaign%20in%20the%20Dholpur%20region%2C%20where%20the%20party%20had%20previously%20won%20six%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%20in%202018.%20This%20time%2C%20Congress%20secured%20five%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%2C%20while%20one%20went%20to%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20two%20to%20BJP.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20political%20dynamics%20since%20the%20last%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20initially%20came%20out%20with%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKam%20Kiya%20Dil%20se%2C%20Gehlot%20Phir%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKam%20kiya%20dil%20se%2C%20Congress%20phir%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20as%20the%20party%20leadership%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20disappoint%20the%20Sachin%20Pilot%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20this%20time%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20influence%20Gurjar%20votes%20in%20the%20state.%20Gurjars%2C%20Jats%2C%20Rajputs%2C%20and%20Meenas%20play%20key%20roles%20in%20forming%20the%20government.%20Gurjars%E2%80%99s%20anger%20is%20palpable%20over%20not%20handing%20over%20the%20reins%20to%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20holds%20influence%20over%20around%2030%20seats%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20Karauli%2C%20Tonk%2C%20Hindaun%2C%20and%20Dausa%20districts%20of%20eastern%20Rajasthan.%20Out%20of%20the%2031%20seats%20that%20the%20Congress%20lost%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20election%2C%2014%20come%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-assembly%2Frajasthan-assembly-election-results-gujjar-disenchantment-costs-the-congress-dearly%2Farticle67602067.ece%5C%22%3Eeastern%20part%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Pilot%E2%80%99s%20community%2C%20the%20Gujjars%2C%20hold%20sway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-profile%20assembly%20seats%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmber%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Satish%20Poonia%2C%20a%20prominent%20Jat%20leader%20and%20former%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20lost%20to%20Prashanth%20Sharma%20by%20a%20margin%20of%209%2C092%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENathdwara%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20C.P.%20Joshi%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20speaker%2C%20faced%20defeat%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20with%20a%20margin%20of%207504%20votes.%20Singh%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20of%20Mewar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKota-North%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%2C%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20managed%20to%20win%20the%20Kota-North%20seat%20with%20a%20narrow%20margin%20of%202%2C000%20votes%20from%20Prahlad%20Gunjal.%20Interestingly%2C%20this%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20Dhariwal%20secured%20the%20seat%20while%20Congress%20didn%E2%80%99t%20win%20the%20state%2C%20as%20he%20typically%20loses%20his%20constituency%20when%20Congress%20loses%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECivil%20Lines%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pratap%20Singh%20Khachariyawas%2C%20another%20minister%20in%20the%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20lost%20his%20seat%20with%20a%20significant%20margin%20of%2028%2C329%20votes%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKaman%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Minister%20Zahida%20Khan%20also%20faced%20defeat%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Nauksham%20Choudhary.%20The%20people%20of%20Deeg%20had%20been%20demanding%20that%20Congress%20not%20give%20a%20ticket%20to%20Zahida%20Khan%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20in%20her%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20prominent%20figures%20such%20as%20Pramod%20Jain%2C%20B.D.%20Kalla%20(Bikaner%20West)%2C%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Jatav%20(Weir)%2C%20Mamta%20Bhupesh%20(Sikr