as%20released%20in%20September%202023%2C%20Moko%20Koza%20celebrates%20his%20Naga%20ancestry%20and%20speaks%20of%20growing%20from%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20soil%20that%20was%20stained%20by%20the%20armies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20the%20stories%20his%20grandmother%20told%20him%20about%20the%20horrors%20visited%20upon%20the%20Naga%20people%20during%20World%20War%20II%20when%20the%20Japanese%20launched%20their%20U-go%20offensive%20into%20India%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20epic%20Battle%20of%20Kohima%20in%201944.%20As%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20music%20video%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20event%20that%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20world%20history.%20An%20event%20that%20tested%20the%20resilience%20of%20the%20Nagas.%20An%20event%20that%20has%20been%20famously%20dubbed%20%E2%80%98The%20Stalingrad%20of%20the%20East%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20children%2C%20my%20grandma%20would%20tell%20us%20stories%20about%20how%20she%20grew%20up%20during%20World%20War%20II%20while%20the%20British%20and%20Japanese%20soldiers%20were%20fighting%20each%20other.%20Most%20of%20our%20stories%20are%20passed%20down%20orally%20from%20one%20generation%20to%20the%20next.%20But%20in%20this%20process%2C%20they%20get%20modified%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20real%20story%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20anymore.%20In%20this%20song%2C%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20get%20the%20real%20story%20recorded%20so%20that%20it%20stays%20on%20forever%20and%20helps%20the%20younger%20generation%20understand%20what%20really%20happened%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20experiment%20with%20new%20sounds%2C%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20our%20folk%20traditions.%20I%20tried%20to%20experiment%20with%20it%20while%20also%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20my%20grandma%20who%20recently%20told%20me%20more%20about%20these%20events%20while%20I%20was%20visiting%2