0never%20a%20life-long%20dream%20for%20Saloni%20Sidana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20by%20education%2C%20she%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20Before%20preparing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20Civil%20Services%20Exam)%2C%20Saloni%20received%20an%20opportunity%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20higher%20studies.%20However%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20stay%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20my%20father%20suggested%20that%20I%20appear%20for%20the%20UPSC%20examination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saloni%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Jalalabad%20town%20in%20Punjab%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20motivation%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20being%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20still%20value%20the%20profession%20of%20a%20doctor.%20The%20commonality%20between%20the%20two%20jobs%20%5Bdoctors%20and%20civil%20servants%5D%20is%20that%20you%20deal%20with%20people.%20Unlike%20many%20other%20professions%20where%20you%20have%20a%20desk%20job%2C%20being%20a%20doctor%20allowed%20me%20to%20deal%20directly%20with%20people%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20after%20you%20become%20a%20public%20servant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20UPSC%20allows%20you%20to%20broaden%20your%20knowledge%20horizon.%20If%20I%20had%20been%20just%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20have%20not%20read%20geography%2C%20civics%2C%20or%20economics.%20During%20preparation%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20about%20my%20country%20in%20detail.%20This%20is%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2035-year-old%2C%20who%20did%20not%20take%20medicine%20as%20her%20optional%20but%20a%20new%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20knowledge%20helped%20her%20crack%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321822%2Fraised-by-single-mom-ias-officer-donge-revaiah-shares-inspiring-upsc-journey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20examination%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20her%20very%20first%20attempt.%20With%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20preparation%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20achieve%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2074.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Saloni%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20Post%20her%20marriage%20with%20IAS%20Ashish%20Vashishta%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20cadre.%20For%20their%20marriage%2C%20Saloni%20paid%20a%20court%20fee%20of%20Rs%20500%20and%20reported%20to%20work%20within%20two%20days.%20She%20has%20been%20praised%20for%20her%20simplicity.%3C%2Fp%